  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libfm-extra</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libfm-extra</application> package contains a library and
other files required by <command>menu-cache-gen</command> libexec of <xref
linkend="menu-cache"/>.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

